cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.SI 

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques for multispectral snapshot demosaicing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves matrix completion and sparse approximation techniques, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with multispectral imaging, which is related to signal processing (cs.MM) and sensing and imaging (cs.SI).
